{"tid":729965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[破壞生態系統] 青海偽三文魚入侵魚類保護區﹗﹗﹗","createTime":"2018-07-05T04:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T01:16:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"64885a036c40b04ba48e6bbc3f3e6d41dfec52b9","tid":729965,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:17:23.000Z","msg":"【青海淡水三文魚入侵魚類保護區】<br />\n【研究員:可能會影響保護區生態系統】<br />\n<br />\n青海人工養殖的的虹鱒魚，早前以國產淡水三文魚之稱，佔據內地三分一市場，一度引起大眾熱烈討論。到近日又再引發爭議。<br />\n<br />\n有漁民在黃河貴德段一個國家級水產種質資源保護區內，發現大量虹鱒魚，懷疑是由上游青海龍羊峽水庫的民澤養殖場逃走出來。　<br />\n<br />\n由於保護區內的魚類大多都是瀕危物種，但虹鱒魚屬於外來肉食性魚類。有研究人員指一旦虹鱒魚適應了保護區的環境，或會佔據了保護區的主要生態功能群，令保護區的保護對象受到很大的威脅，影響整個保護區的生態系統。<br />\n<br />\n民澤養殖場去年已因糞便飼料污染水質，而被要求整改。這次又被漁民投訴對大量虹鱒魚流入保護區置之不理。研究人員就希望養殖場盡快處理相關問題。　<br />\n<br />\n#青海虹鱒魚養殖場<br />\n#魚類保護區<br />\n#生態系統<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n&lt;iframe src=&quot;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1774318446045967%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=560&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fcablechinadesk%252Fvideos%252F1774318446045967%252F%26show_text%3D0%26width%3D560%22&d=Vkdv0jVFtJcBGtldFPmmHxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=61aa35dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1774318446045967%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=560&quot;</a> width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; style=&quot;border:none;overflow:hidden&quot; scrolling=&quot;no&quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowTransparency=&quot;true&quot; allowFullScreen=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;"},{"pid":"eaad47c43f2bdc19bfe20209f997d6f2b5f4d210","tid":729965,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T04:21:00.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲養嘅魚都變蝗"},{"pid":"296d4a94e2c03897a4d70bb14c7cad1afd599a2d","tid":7299